title: Git Pull Request Workflow

participant Developer as Dev
participant Local Git as Git
participant GitHub as GH
participant CI/CD as CI
participant Reviewer as Rev
participant Main Branch as Main

Dev->>Git: git checkout -b feature/login
Dev->>Git: git commit -m "Add login form"
Dev->>Git: git commit -m "Add validation"
Dev->>Git: git push origin feature/login
Git->>GH: Push branch (2 commits)
Dev->>GH: Create Pull Request
note over GH: PR #42: Add login feature
GH->>CI: Trigger checks
CI->>CI: Run tests (87 passed)
CI->>CI: Run linter (0 warnings)
CI-->>GH: All checks passed
GH->>Rev: Request review
Rev->>GH: Review code
Rev-->>GH: Comment: "Add error handling"
GH-->>Dev: Review: changes requested
Dev->>Git: git commit -m "Add error handling"
Dev->>Git: git push origin feature/login
Git->>GH: Push (1 new commit)
GH->>CI: Re-trigger checks
CI-->>GH: All checks passed
GH->>Rev: Re-request review
Rev-->>GH: Approve
Dev->>GH: Squash and merge
GH->>Main: Merge PR #42
note over Main: feature/login merged
GH->>CI: Trigger deploy pipeline
